name: multi result test
baseQuery:
SELECT ?x ?y WHERE
	{ 
		?x a test:A .
		?x test:hasValue STRING_VALUE .
		?x test:hasValue2 ?y .
		FILTER(?y=INT_VALUE) .
  }
mapping:
BASE <http://www.symbiote-h2020.eu/ontology/semanticmapping/testModel#>

	RULE 
		CONDITION CLASS :A :hasValue VALUE ="test" AND :hasValue2 VALUE =42  
		PRODUCTION CLASS :B :hasValue2 VALUE :instanceOfB
